com.sun.identity.saml2.assertion.impl

Class EncryptedAssertionImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.saml2.assertion.impl.EncryptedElementImpl
      • com.sun.identity.saml2.assertion.impl.EncryptedAssertionImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EncryptedAssertion, EncryptedElement

    public class EncryptedAssertionImpl
extends EncryptedElementImpl
implements EncryptedAssertion
    The EncryptedAssertion represents an assertion in encrypted fashion, as defined by the XML Encryption Syntax and Processing specification [XMLEnc]. The EncryptedAssertion contains an EncryptedData and zero or more EncryptedKeys.
